<HEADLINE> New Highway Opens To Traffic </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANNING, March 5 (Xinhua) -- National Highway No.321 opened
to traffic today with the completion of construction of the
33.45-km section located in the Sanjiang Dong Nationality
Autonomous County, Guizhou Province.
</P>
<P>
The new highway links Guangzhou, capital of south China's
Guangdong Province, with Chengdu, capital of Sichuan Province.
</P>
<P>
The section was carried out over a six year period, with
engineers overcoming extremely difficult topographical conditions.
</P>
<P>
The highway is expected to spark local economic growth in the
vast backward southwestern area which is densely populated with
members of ethnic minorities. 
</P>
</TEXT>
