present, he would send a strong delegation, the official news
agency quoted Annan as saying.
</P>
<P>
The U.N. chief expressed his desire following invitation
extended to him and the Security Council by the Committee of Five
on Sierra Leone under the Economic Community of West African
States (ECOWAS) to attend the ceremony billed for March 10.
</P>
