<P>
JOHANNESBURG, March 5 (Xinhua) -- South African mining giant
De Beers is ready to invest in the development of new diamond
deposits in Russia, South African Press Association reported
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The news agency quoted De Beers as saying that it is just
waiting for the right investment conditions.
</P>
<P>
