<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 5 (Xinhua) -- South Korea plans to buy 12
sophisticated launch and guidance systems for Standard anti-ship
missiles at a cost of 214 million U.S dollars, the Pentagon said
in a statement on Thursday.
</P>
