their efforts in order to contribute for the preservation of
peace, security and stability in the continent.
</P>
<P>
With regard to the situation in Somalia, the two ministers
have underlined the necessity for the Somali people to engage in
direct and peaceful political dialogue in order to bring about a
just and lasting peace in that country.
</P>
<P>
The ministers have, to this end, called upon the international
community to render the required political, financial and moral
support to bring to an end the suffering of the people of
Somalia.
</P>
