<TEXT>
<P>
GUILIN, March 6 (Xinhua) -- China Southern Airlines plans to
start an international flight between Guilin, one of the
pictureque cities in south China's Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous
Region, and Fukuoka, Japan.
</P>
<P>
