<HEADLINE> U.S. Firm to Produce Filters at East China Plant </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SUZHOU, March 6 (Xinhua) -- A new filter firm went operational
today in Suzhou Industrial Park, in east China's Jiangsu Province.
</P>
