<HEADLINE> Ethiopia's Economy Sound, PM </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, March 6 (Xinhua) -- Ethiopian Prime Minister
Meles Zenawi said the nation is in a much stable position
economically with inflation as low as 0.25 percent over the last
six months.
</P>
