understanding and cooperation agreement, and they carried on a
joint manoeuvre to test Mozambican military's capability in
response to the emergent actions in July and August in 1996.
</P>
<P>
It is reported that U.S. has helped train Mozambican officials
and offered some military materials, including vehicles.
</P>
<P>
Mozambique got independence in 1975 and started reforming the
military forces with the help of western powers on the basis of
the formerly Soviet Union military structure.  
